description.content:
Located in Bacolod, 1.5 km from Negros Museum, OYO 543 Negrense Suites provides accommodation with a restaurant, free private parking, a bar and a shared lounge. With free WiFi, this 2-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and room service.

Panaad Stadium is 6 km from the hotel, while Mambukal Zipline is 27 km away. The nearest airport is New Bacolod-Silay Airport, 3.6 km from OYO 543 Negrense Suites.

OYO 517 Jcad Hotel Lahug features air-conditioned rooms with cable flat-screen TV in the Lahug district of Cebu City. This 2-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and room service. SM City Cebu is 3 km from the hotel and Fuente Osmena Circle is 4 km away.

With a private bathroom equipped with a bidet and free toiletries, rooms at the hotel also have a city view.

Situated conveniently in the Quezon City district of Manila, OYO 430 Michael's Place is set 13 km from Smart Araneta Coliseum, 17 km from Malacanang Palace and 17 km from SM Megamall. With a restaurant, the 2-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. Rizal Park is 19 km from the hotel and Power Plant Mall is 21 km away.

At the hotel, all rooms come with a desk and a flat-screen TV.

Languages spoken at the 24-hour front desk include Filipino and English.

Madrid-Barajas. También se encuentra cerca de la estación de metro de Cuzco (línea 10) y de la estación de metro de Tetuán (línea 1). Cuenta con multitud de líneas de autobús que discurren por el Paseo de la Castellana y por la Calle Bravo Murillo y que conectan la zona con todo Madrid. Entre 

El establecimiento ofrece WiFi gratuito y aparcamiento privado. Posee, además, patio, vistas al jardín y restaurante.

Las habitaciones tienen TV de pantalla plana y algunas incluyen zona de estar, mientras que otras disponen de terraza o patio. Todas son climatizadas con aire acondicionado y calefacción central.

La recepción permanece abierta las 24 horas.

Offering a year-round outdoor pool, barbecue and children's playground, Blackstone Country Villages Hotel is situated in Villa General Belgrano, 6 km from Brewer Park Villa General Belgrano. Free WiFi is featured throughout the property and free private parking is available on site.

Each room at this hotel is air conditioned and has a flat-screen TV with cable channels. Some rooms feature a seating area to relax in after a busy day. A balcony or patio are featured in certain rooms. Every room has a private bathroom with a bidet and shower, with free toiletries provided.

Selina Miami River is surrounded by pastel-colored, 1920s Old Florida bungalows transporting you back to a simpler time. Immerse yourself in wellness, workshops, and more in this haven for escape. Head to The Lawn for weekly Sunday BBQs, yoga classes paired with traveling DJs, picnics and movie nights. Enjoy the flavorful Latin cuisine and hand-crafted cocktails from the on-site bungalow. Selina Miami River is the perfect backdrop for your Miami getaway.

This unassuming hotel is on a residential side street 200 m from Route 3. It's 6 km from Phayun Beach and 8 km from Wat Khlong Sai, a Buddhist temple.
Accommodations include co-ed and female-only dorms sleeping up to 6 people, plus casual rooms and studios; all feature free Wi-Fi. Rooms add flat-screen TVs and DVD players, along with microwaves and minifridges. They also come with balconies offering city and/or distant countryside views. Studios provide kitchenettes.
Hot breakfast is available for a fee and served in a low-key bar/restaurant. Other amenities include a fitness center. Massage is available.

description.content: All travellers seem to be fall in love Da Nang city from the first time they arrive. Da Nang not only impresses visitors with dynamic image, always full of vitality, but also is attracted by the poetic natural beauty, enchanting with immense sky and sea and mountains. When traveling, we can't help mentioning the paradise of convalescence in this beautiful city and the SANTA LUXURY HOTEL is one of them. With 65 elegantly designed rooms with unique neoclassical style with a slightly European orientation, new modern rooms will bring you an unforgettable experience here. The rooftop swimming pool is also a highlight of Santa Luxury Hotel when you can just soak in the clear blue water while watching the panoramic view of My Khe beach - the beach voted by Forbes magazine as one of 10 charming beaches on the planet. In addition, the service from the room to the restaurant, spa, swimming pool will bring you great experiences in Da Nang. It only takes 2 minutes to walk from the hotel to My Khe beach, 5km to the airport, 3km to Han Market. In addition, the hotel also provides car rental services or tours to attractive destination such as Ba Na Hills, Hoi An, Ngu Hanh Son, My Son Holy Land, Cu Lao Cham ... with extremely affordable prices.

The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, an ATM and currency exchange for guests.

An American breakfast is available each morning at the hotel.

Ho Chi Minh City Museum is 1.8 km from Saigon 1979 Hotel, while Ben Thanh Market is 2.1 km from the property. The nearest airport is Tan Son Nhat International Airport, 13 km from the accommodation.

Featuring a restaurant, a bar and a garden, Ginis Beach Resort is located in Kamala Beach and is a 16-minute walk from Kamala Beach. This 3-star hotel offers room service. The hotel has family rooms.

All rooms include air conditioning and a flat-screen TV, and some rooms at the hotel have a balcony.

Ginis Beach Resort offers a buffet or Asian breakfast.

The accommodation has a terrace.

Laem Sing Beach is 2.7 km from Ginis Beach Resort, while Phuket FantaSea is 1.9 km from the property. The nearest airport is Phuket International Airport, 27.4 km from the hotel.

We are taking extra cleanliness and hygiene measures. Your safety is our priority.

The Hotel Cristal Setúbal is a new 4-stars hotel that enjoys a central location. The hotel is located just 1500 meters from what is considered the city's main avenue, Avenida Luisa Todi.

The hotel's 85 rooms with a contemporary and glamorous decor, lead us to an environment of peace, calm and tranquility. All have air conditioning, a minibar, a flat-screen TV and a safe. It should be noted that the hotel has Standard, Terrace, Suite, Junior Suite and rooms adapted for people with disabilities.
The Hotel Cristal Setúbal offers free Wi-Fi in all areas and has a 24-hour reception, available to provide you with a range of services, including: shuttle service, car rental, taxi service and storage luggage. It also has private parking open 24 hours a day ( at an additional cost ), the Cristal restaurant with a capacity for more than 200 people, a luxurious Bar where you can taste the traditional Moscatel of Setúbal and two multifunctional rooms ( events / conferences ).

Escape to an alpine paradise of world-class skiing, blue ribbon fishing, majestic golf courses, hundreds of miles of trails to explore, only steps away from Canyons Ski Resort slopes, and walking distance from the charming shops, art galleries, and award-winning restaurants of downtown. Start your day with a walk in the cool mountain air, savor your favorite seasonal adventure, then soak the starry night away from a pair of outdoor hot tubs.

Club Wyndham Park City features spacious one- and two-bedroom resort suites that comfortably sleep four to eight guests at 763 to 963 square feet. Suites feature one king bed in the master, two double beds in the guest room and a queen sleeper sofa in the living area. You will appreciate separate bedrooms, a full kitchen and the convenience of a washer/dryer in each suite. You will also enjoy separate living/dining areas and TVs throughout.

Find us just eight miles from MIA Airport – easily accessible with our free shuttle. Dolphin Mall and Miami International Mall can be reached in six minutes by car. Downtown and CityPlace Doral are both within a 10-minute drive. We're only 1.5 miles to Jackson Memorial. Enjoy free WiFi and a heated outdoor pool at our pet friendly hotel. Breakfast is on us.

description.content:
Located in Rawai Beach, 2.7 km from Rawai Beach, Lotus Bleu Resort & Restaurant provides air-conditioned rooms and a garden. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and a tour desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The resort has an outdoor swimming pool and pool views, and guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant or a drink at the bar.

Guest rooms at the resort are equipped with a seating area and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. The rooms include a desk.

An American breakfast is available daily at Lotus Bleu Resort & Restaurant.
The accommodation has a terrace.

Phuket Seashell Museum is 3.2 km from Lotus Bleu Resort & Restaurant, while Windmill Viewpoint is 5.3 km away. The nearest airport is Phuket International, 45.1 km from the resort, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.

Almost completely surrounded by mountains, this scenic community of Park City is more than a ski town. In summer months the slopes turn into the best mountain biking and hiking hills around.
WorldMark Park City offers spacious two-, three-, and four-bedroom resort suites that comfortably sleep six to ten guests in 1,258 - 2,230 square feet. Suites feature one king bed in the master, with a variety of beds for the guest rooms, and a sleeper sofa in the living area or loft. You will appreciate the privacy of separate bedrooms and the economy of a full kitchen that allows you to save money on eating out when you can cook up a tasty meal for the entire family from your suite! Plus, separate living/dining areas, a fireplace and a private balcony/terrace in every suite.

description.content:
Located in Danang, a 5-minute walk from My Khe Beach, Kiwi Hotel & Apartments provides accommodations with a restaurant, free private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a shared lounge. Featuring family rooms, this property also provides guests with a terrace. The property has a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests.

All guest rooms features air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a fridge, an electric tea pot, a bidet, a hairdryer and a desk. Rooms come complete with a private bathroom equipped with a shower and free toiletries, while some units at the hotel also provide guests with a seating area. The rooms feature a closet.

Pousada Recanto das Águas features a restaurant, outdoor swimming pool, a bar and garden in Fama. Among the facilities at this property are a 24-hour front desk and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. Private parking can be arranged at an extra charge.

The units in the guest house are equipped with a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. At Pousada Recanto das Águas all rooms are equipped with air conditioning and a private bathroom.

Guests at the accommodation can enjoy a buffet breakfast.

Pousada Recanto das Águas offers a children's playground.

Alfenas is 19 km from the guest house.

OYO Hotel Antonialli is located 2 km from the center of Itumbiara and just 1 km from the bus station.The hotel is 5 km from Juscelino Kubitschek Municipal Stadium. The nearest airport is in Uberlândia, 130 km away.

The rooms have a TV and air conditioning, as well as a private bathroom. Superior rooms also have a minibar, while some rooms have a minibar and cable channels.

A breakfast buffet is served daily and includes various seasonal fruits, breads and cold meats, as well as a variety of hot and cold drinks. Private parking is free, as is Wifi.

Location
OYO Hotel Los Valles is located in Ocoyoacac, State of Mexico. On the Mexico-Toluca highway very close to La Marquesa Park.

Special Features
It has the rustic charm of a hotel in the forest, a garden and parking. It offers breakfast, laundry service and horse rental to tour La Marquesa.

Facilities
The rooms are clean and spacious. They have free Wi-Fi and a private bathroom.

Nearby
1 km from La Marquesa Park and 3 km from Salazar Lagoon. Lic. Adolfo Lopez Mateos Airport is 25 km away.

Just a 12-minute walk from Divino Salvador Parish and Malinalco Main Square, OYO Hotel Marmil Cerca del Hospital Malínalco offers its guests a free American breakfast and outdoor pool, as well as massage services also available.Set in a chalet-style building, this property offers comfortable accommodation with rustic decor and wooden furniture. All rooms are equipped with cable TV and a fan, as well as a private bathroom with shower.The restaurant at OYO Hotel Marmil Cerca del Hospital Malínalco only offers breakfast service and specializes in Mexican dishes. Guests can find other dining options within a 10-minute walk towards the city center.The city of Toluca is a 70-minute drive from the OYO Hotel Marmil around the Hospital Malínalco and Mexico City can be visited in about 1 hour and 45 minutes by car.

Quinta Sao Francisco offers accommodation full of charm, with updates and modern decorations.
It has furniture, old decorations, agricultural materials that will make you relive old times. Guests can soak up the sun by the pool or hike over the mountain or soak in the vineyard. Other activities include hiking, cycling, tennis.

description.content:
Located in Dubai's Barsha Heights neighborhood, it is easily accessible by public transport on which the nearest bus stop is 150 metres away and is only a kilometre away from Dubai Internet City Metro Station. The property allows easy access to all this destination has to offer as it is located within 4 kilometres from the city centre and main entertainment areas.

All 447 units come with tiled floors and features a fully equipped kitchenette with a microwave, fridge, stove top, a dining area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, and a private bathroom with shower and a hairdryer.

Guests at the hotel apartment can enjoy a buffet or a halal breakfast as the hotel takes pride in offering a choice of dining facilities which serve delicious culinary specialities. A kids' club is also available for guests at Millennium Place Barsha Heights Hotel Apartments.

name.content: Millennium Place Barsha Heights Hotel Apartments

description.content:
Situated in Miami Beach, 650 feet from Jewish Museum of Florida, Casa Sofi features rooms with air conditioning and free WiFi. The property is around 0.9 miles from Versace Mansion, 1.6 miles from Lincoln Road and 1.7 miles from New World Center. The property is allergy-free and is located less than 0.6 miles from South Pointe Park.

At the hotel, rooms come with a wardrobe. At Casa Sofi rooms have a desk, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom.

Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Ocean Drive, Art Deco Historic District and Lummus Park. The nearest airport is Miami Seaplane Base Airport, 3.7 miles from Casa Sofi.

This is our guests' favourite part of Miami Beach, according to independent reviews.

We speak your language!

Inspired by their worldly travels, the owners of RSVP Hotel Bozeman are taking things to the next level in Montana. Located in Midtown Bozeman, what was once the Rainbow Hotel has been meticulously resurrected to change the way you stay and play in this mountain town.  Great taste makes you feel good, and that's what you should expect from The Farmer's Daughters Cafe & Eatery. Located in the heart of RSVP Hotel BZN, this cafe takes you through the fields and farms of Montana with each fresh ingredient.

Stickney's is open 11:30am-2pm & 5:30pm-9pm. The Grille Fri-Sun 11am-4pm. The Main Dining Room is available for dine in breakfast Mon-Fri 7am-10am & Sat-Sun from 7am11am; dinner Thur-Sun 5:30pm-9pm & cocktails 9pm-11pm Fri & Sat only.  Rosebrook Bar Mon-Fri 3pm-9pm & Sat-Sun 12pm-9pm. Morsels is open 7am-12pm, take-out only.
